      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOLLIES HAYLEY (1) showed good early burn but run over late to finish 7th at Taree Super Track in Grade 5 company. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Can make amends. BLACK BOOK IT (4) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (30.32) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Shapes as one to consider. LAST KEY (7) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished in the minors latest when second (23.39) at this track and may be close to breaking through. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Leading player again. IRINKA ALEX (3) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
